(author: jayem)
(date: 2026)
(Store laser beam plane Z and optional approach / max-travel.)
(#1 = BEAM Z G53 mm, #2 = approach above beam mm, #3 = max travel below beam mm)
(Uses #5504-#5506 — NOT G30 #5184-#5186.)

o<laser_set_beam_z> sub
    #5504 = #1
    o<sbz_app> if [#2 GT 0]
      #5505 = #2
    o<sbz_app> endif
    o<sbz_trv> if [#3 GT 0]
      #5506 = #3
    o<sbz_trv> endif
    (DEBUG, LASER: BEAM Z=#5504 approach=#5505 travel=#5506)
o<laser_set_beam_z> endsub

M2
